hopobject.body: Three years rx-meds.net Rihanna in a bikini kicking around a soccer ball? Score! The 25-year-old singer continued to cause a commotion during her trip to Barbados, this time hitting the beach to play a wet and wild game of soccer in the sand on Aug. 8, 2013. RiRi suited up in a string bikini and flashy gold body chain as she relaxed by the water with her friends and family. It's been a non-stop party for Rihanna, who arrived in her native Barbados to celebrate the island's Crop Over Festival earlier in August. Check out more photos from her trip ...
